**Instruction_Field:** Natural Language Processing mein word embeddings ke istemal ki wazahat karein

**Input_Field:** 

**Output_Field:** Word embeddings Natural Language Processing (NLP) ke liye sab se powerful tools mein se aik hain. Yeh alfaaz ya phrases ki mathematical numayindagi hoti hai vector space mein, jis se alfaaz ke darmiyan mushabihat aur un ke istemal ke context ko measure kiya ja sakta hai. Word embeddings sentiment analysis, text classification, sequence mein agla lafz predict karne, aur synonyms aur analogies ko samajhne jaise tasks ke liye mufeed hain. Yeh alfaaz ko numerical values ki soorat mein process karne ki sahulat deti hain, jis se machines NLP tasks asani se anjaam de sakti hain.

Is ka matlab hai ke companies data owners ki wazeh ijazat ke baghair unka personal data collect aur use nahi kar sakti. Is tareeqe se users ko yeh ikhtiyar milta hai ke woh khud faisla karein ke unka konsa data companies use kar sakti hain aur kis maqsad ke liye. Companies ko chahiye ke woh yeh bhi wazeh karein ke woh collected data ko kaise istemal kar rahi hain, taake users soch samajh kar faisla kar sakein aur apne data par control rakh sakein.

**Instruction_Field:** Cogging torque ka concept wazahat se bayan karein.

**Input_Field:** 

**Output_Field:** Cogging torque woh torque hai jo aik ghoomnay wali device par tab lagta hai jab device ko us se judi hui gears ke daanton ki taraf se muzahimat ka samna hota hai. Cogging torque us waqt paida hota hai jab gear drive ke daant aapas mein mesh karte hain to reaction force generate hoti hai. Yeh force aapas mein ek dosray ko dhakelti hai, jis se ek drag force paida hoti hai jo gears se shaft tak muntakil hoti hai. Cogging torque ki miqdaar daanton ke size aur tadaad, gear ke material aur design par mabni hoti hai. Aksar motorized applications mein cogging torque pasandeeda nahi hota kyun ke yeh efficiency mein kami ka sabab banta hai. Cogging torque ko kam karne ke liye gear designs ko aksar symmetrical banaya jata hai ya phir kuch khaas tooth profiles istemal ki jati hain jo daanton ke aapas mein takraane par force of contact ko kam kar deti hain.

**Instruction_Field:** Plants mein cellular respiration ka amal wazahat se bayan karein.

**Input_Field:** 

**Output_Field:** Plants mein cellular respiration aik pechida amal hai jismein plant glucose ko istemal hone wali energy mein tabdeel karta hai. Yeh amal tab shuru hota hai jab plant environment se carbon dioxide leta hai aur usay paani ke sath mila kar, sunlight ki energy istemal karte hue, glucose molecules banata hai. Yeh glucose phir mazeed tod kar carbon dioxide aur paani ke seedha molecules mein tabdeel kiya jata hai. Is amal ke dauran, jo energy release hoti hai, usay adenosine triphosphate (ATP) molecules banane ke liye istemal kiya jata hai. ATP plant ke dusre amaliyat jaise growth aur reproduction ko power dene ke liye istemal hota hai. Is ke ilawa, ATP ko mazeed tod kar heat energy bhi hasil ki ja sakti hai, jo plant ke temperature ko barqarar rakhne mein madad deti hai. Is amal mein paida hone wale carbon dioxide aur paani ke molecules dobara environment mein release kar diye jate hain taake yeh cycle mukammal ho sake.

**Instruction_Field:** Deforestation ke nataij bayan kijiye.

**Input_Field:** 

**Output_Field:** Deforestation janglaat ko saaf aur khatam karne ka amal hai. Deforestation ke nataij mein mitti ki katayi, pani ki quality mein kami, biodiversity ka kam hona, atmosphere mein carbon dioxide ka barhna aur wildlife ke liye habitat ka khatam hona shamil hain. Jab darakht jo pani aur mitti ko rokne mein madad karte hain hata diye jate hain, to mitti ke zarraat beh kar nikal jate hain, jis se soil erosion hoti hai. Is se daryaaon aur streams mein silt jama ho sakta hai, jo pani ki quality ko mutasir karta hai aur flood ka sabab ban sakta hai. Is ke ilawa, jab darakht hata diye jate hain, to wildlife apna habitat kho deti hai. Is se kai qisam ki species endangered ho sakti hain, jis se biodiversity aur bhi kam ho jati hai. Deforestation ki wajah se atmosphere mein carbon dioxide bhi barh jati hai kyun ke kam darakht photosynthesis ke zariye is gas ko absorb karte hain, jo climate change mein izafa kar sakta hai.

**Instruction_Field:** Diye gaye number ka square root nikalain.

**Input_Field:** 

**Output_Field:** def sqrt(n):
    low = 0
    high = n
    
    while low <= high:
        mid = (low + high) // 2
        if mid * mid == n:
            return mid
        elif mid * mid < n:
            low = mid + 1
        else:
            high = mid - 1
            
    return low - 1

  "instruction": "Linked list ko reverse karein.",
  "input": "",
  "output": "def reverse(head): 
    prev = None
    cur = head 

    while cur:
        next = cur.next
        cur.next = prev 
        prev = cur 
        cur = next
    head = prev
    
    return head"
}

{
  "instruction": "Aik algorithm design karein jo stock buy aur sell ka maximum profit nikal sake?",
  "input": "",
  "output": "def maxProfit(prices):
    min_price = float('inf')
    max_profit = 0

    for price in prices:
        min_price = min(min_price, price) 
        profit = price - min_price
        max_profit = max(max_profit, profit)

    return max_profit"
}

**Instruction_Field:** Wazahat kariye ke random forest algorithm kis tarah individual decision trees se zyada accuracy hasil karta hai.

**Input_Field:** 

**Output_Field:** Random forest aik ensemble-based tareeqa hai jo individual decision trees se zyada accuracy hasil karta hai. Yeh multiple decision trees ki predictions ko ensemble approach ke zariye aggregate karta hai. Har decision tree apni alag prediction deta hai, aur in individual predictions ko ya to probabilities average kar ke ya majority vote le kar combine kiya jata hai. Is tareeqe se decision trees ki predictions ka variance kam ho jata hai, jis se final predictions zyada accurate hoti hain. Is ke ilawa, yeh overfitting ko bhi kam karta hai kyun ke har tree ki independent decisions ko combine kiya jata hai, jis se random fluctuations smooth ho jati hain.

**Instruction_Field:** Wazahat karein ke trade protectionism kisi mulk ki economy ko nuqsan kaise pohcha sakta hai.

**Input_Field:** 

**Output_Field:** Trade protectionism ka matlab hai ke domestic industries ko foreign competition se bachane ke liye tariffs ya doosri pabandiyan lagana. Yeh amal us mulk ki economy ke liye nuqsan deh ho sakta hai jo isay istemal karta hai, kyun ke is se imported cheezon ki cost barh jati hai, jo consumers ke liye un cheezon ko kam dastiyab banata hai. Is se un cheezon ki demand kam ho jati hai, jis ki wajah se sales aur domestic producers ki aamdani bhi kam ho jati hai. Protectionism ki wajah se domestic companies ko innovate karne ya zyada behtar hone ka incentive bhi kam ho jata hai, jis se market mein inefficiency paida hoti hai. Aakhir mein, protectionism mulkon ke darmiyan economic tension bhi paida kar sakta hai, jis ki wajah se retaliatory tariffs lagte hain jo trade ko mazeed restrict kar dete hain.
